    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员期待美国 CPI 支撑半个百分点的降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/bond-traders-look-to-us-cpi-to-buttress-half-point-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[那些希望在国债市场获得更多收益的投资者正在等待美国通胀数据，以支持美联储加快降息步伐的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/bond-traders-look-to-us-cpi-to-buttress-half-point-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
