    <item>
      <title>中国贷款下降引发“资产负债表”衰退担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国近二十年来首次缩减银行贷款，引发人们担忧中国这一全球第二大经济体正像日本几十年前那样陷入“资产负债表衰退”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
